name: The Aqualad
description:
Size: 12" x 8"

Skill Level:
Adult: Intermediate to Advanced.
Youth: Beginner to Advanced

This design is one of my favorites! It has a slight single concave to give you a little more lift and allows this handplane to accelerate very quickly and retain a great deal of speed. The wider tail give you more planing surface and support and the diamond tail helps give it a little more control. This is a very versatile board. The smaller size of this model makes it easier to swim, and puts less strain on your arm and shoulder. 
Each handplane is custom made to order. When you place an order please specify which colors you would like. Additional fees apply to more than 2 colors, cloth inlays, Go-Pro mounts, Cut-laps, ect. If you have any questions please contact me. Ahoi!

The bottom contour has a slight single concave that transitions into a unique double step that gives the board even more speed!

name: Add a Color
description: So, you say you love what you see but want to pick your own colors? No worries! Each Ahoi! Handplane is made to YOUR custom order up to two colors. Add an extra color for an addition fee of only 5 bucks!

name: Cloth Inlay
description: Whats that? Well, a cloth inlay is a fabric that is glassed onto your handplane! Say for instance, your favorite old t-shirt, an old flannel, or even your old blanket that you just cant part with. We can even provide wood-grain inlays or patterned inlays like the sample shown. If you want an inlay but don't know what you want, just tell me your favorite colors and I'll provide one for you. It's just a neat way to personalize your Ahoi! Handplane!!!

name: GoPro Mount
description: Add an FCS plug to the nose of your custom handplane for mounting a GoPro Camera.

name: Cut-Lap
description: Add a Cut-lap to accentuate the color of your resin art

name: Resin Pin Stripe
description: Accent your handplanes color with a color resin pin stripe!
